overview: The Mass of the Gnostic Catholic Church, A Eucharistic Ritual by Aleister Crowley. Sponsored by Anahata Chapter of the O.T.O. Rose Croix, with the sanction of the United States Grand Lodge, O.T.O. Shot on location at Horizon Lodge in Seattle, Washington in September of 2013.
title: Liber XV: The Gnostic Mass
